Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.64,0:01:28.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.12,0:01:42.33,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.40,0:01:52.36,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.59,0:02:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}精打細算的亞力克斯\NCalculate Alex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，把板手拿給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝了，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,板手找到了，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.55,0:02:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我記得你不是槍兵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械你會修嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家我也是有知識有技術的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比普通的機械師要可靠多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.76,0:02:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個好消息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既然是機械師就早說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N這下總算可以有個後輩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.41,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊\N其實我只是個槍兵而已呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對機械是一竅不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.74,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先這套制服得想點辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械師就要有機械師的樣子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次不是救了你們嗎\N這次換你們來救我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要麻煩人家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲等合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍，從現在起你就是\N銀之戰艦維修班的一員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他表現得不夠高興哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興就給我笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你找到新的工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，副艦長有事找你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說蘇菲亞小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.59,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八小時耐力賽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說銀之戰艦現在\N正在駛往地平洞窟嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道地平洞窟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是先鋒艇駕駛員\N沒有人會不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的八小時耐力賽\N是每個人都想挑戰的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N一個有點與眾不同的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽必須使用\N現場所準備的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.11,0:04:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了想辦法\N讓破爛不堪的先鋒艇飛起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在當場進行調整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零點的時候\N飛在最前面的機體就算冠軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重點是必須持續飛八個小時哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是駕駛員而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也考驗了機械師的本領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有團隊合作的趣味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要不要參加比賽看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以參加嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，只要你們有那個意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們只有兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.81,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼組隊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會派葛溫他們跟著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.31,0:04:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就能參加了耶，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，我們參加吧，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒妳也是跟我們一隊的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不瞞妳說\N當我決心留在這裡時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已經放棄參加比賽的念頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我實在很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，蘇菲亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.97,0:05:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去做出賽的準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會覺得\N沒辦法再參加比賽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡\N駕駛先鋒艇就是為了戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是銀之戰艦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回這片天空真正的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遲早有一天必須借重你們這些\N先鋒艇駕駛員的力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這天一定會來到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.00,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，請小心慢走\N銀之戰艦就交給我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只需要想著比賽的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才塔台那裡傳來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺無赦的\N銀之戰艦一行人抵達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺無赦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來今夜會是個\N難得的開心之夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諾茲侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.18,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下角色都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戲可以開幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走向毀滅的最後一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大的沙漏呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，還不快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第225屆地平洞窟\N八小時耐力賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇抽選即將開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位駕駛員集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要抽到一架好機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛技術比較重要啦\N我們也去吧，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.22,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色六號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自奧格蘭的戴姆與卡多加隊\N抽到的是藍色六號的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是黑色十號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是來自諾齊亞的\N克勞士與拉薇隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒妳去抽籤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去抽出最好的籤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是位可愛的先鋒艇駕駛員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這東西飛得起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比傳聞中的還要慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼破成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.88,0:08:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說每年只有個位數的機體\N能夠飛完全程呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忍不住手癢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟們，幹活囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可有得忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得在三個小時裡\N讓這傢伙飛得起來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我們也來，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是被我打過分數的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打分數…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，那邊鎖緊一點\N聽說妳們沒抽中好機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過魏斯洛隊長\N有我們幫忙就沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小子叫莫藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是個剛出爐的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是從克勞索拉斯號\N跳槽過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫藍‧謝蘭度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個都很可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.26,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比女的先鋒艇駕駛員\N更恐怖的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就會認清她的真面目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比賽期間\N我會負責照顧艾兒薇絲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她一直不肯\N離開那兩個孩子身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好先讓你的眼晴\N適應一下黑暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,零點準時動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，他們只會礙手礙腳而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和業餘的一起飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個領航員\N在前些日子的戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還會發生紅視現象\N太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是在玩家家酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的就是這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在著急什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說塔琪安娜‧魏斯洛\N不過就是這種程度的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是自找罪受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好可憐哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的是我們好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒她就要把\N氣出在我們身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她長得那麼可愛的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是不能靠外表來判斷的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,譬如說那邊那位伊薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人為什麼老是在生氣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要飛起來的話\N乾脆重新組裝比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下不徹底改裝可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.78,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確\N連機身架構都受損成這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但會讓機翼搖晃\N操縱桿也會變重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子比原先想像得還難處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.92,0:10:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.13,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克勞士你們好厲害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒妳也是個\N很厲害的機械師呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.93,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可以向旋風霍克炫耀了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.65,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我們參加了這個比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要炫耀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了也要跟\N大肥雞和鼻毛小子炫耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用這架\N第一次乘坐的機體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這第一次飛的比賽路線上\N飛完全程的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就表示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們作為駕駛員的本事\N也更上了一層樓吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也向大風暴區\N更邁進了一步對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？我聽不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說要好好努力比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，一起努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK！克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒，我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來很有精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是去把事情做個處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇她會成為一個\N頂尖的機械師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.97,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.15,0:12:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，我現在飛在\N地平洞窟裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油，克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，新來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了，你坐在那裡不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有上廁所的時候才可以離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面裝了什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了魏斯洛隊長好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個單純的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.70,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能擁有像你這麼好的後輩\N我實在太幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於比賽的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要設施的警備\N要比想像中來得更嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是按照當初的計畫進行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩妳了，塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果狀況有變\N我會立刻見機行事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍賣會那邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18：00，開始時間沒有變更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.76,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三，二，一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次作戰需要的是準確性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.22,0:13:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想見你，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我家的克勞士做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是那個時候\N發生紅視現象的女孩是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.07,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪奧殿下，我覺得您還是\N先報上自己的名字比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.61,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，我是迪奧‧艾拉克萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣\N你都已經被我擊落兩次了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你都忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你是基爾特公會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？基爾特公會！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.37,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來打聲招呼而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會把艾兒交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.25,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我倒是完全無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比較想和你\N在比賽裡飛個高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果英麥曼你要出場的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想拿出真本事來比比看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字不叫英麥曼好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說你是英麥曼\N你就是英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我贏了\N你就把你的名字告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常應該是說輸了才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可能輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魯修拉，我們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳是那個時候\N駕駛紅色那架的人對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要來妨礙我們\N隨便飛飛就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍然要維持原定計畫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要變更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被個難搞的傢伙纏上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底是來幹嘛的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可是敵人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的很開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好我有跟著戴芬妮一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.31,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被您姊姊聽到了\N不曉得她會怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.08,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要向戴芬妮好好道謝就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那人最喜歡聽人奉承了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位戴芬妮姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長她太亂來了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連引擎都還沒熱說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.94,0:16:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成是那個基爾特小子\N踩到她哪根神經了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.61,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是引擎的問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才明明還好好的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒艇壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我爭口氣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞管裡面的空氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已經排乾淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,節流管的狀況呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.79,0:17:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用慌張，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，一定可以起動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞情況怎樣，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次相當的安定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個瞌睡蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.38,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲，瞌睡蟲加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.51,0:17:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍你不要給我亂跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強，首先要先習慣一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.62,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不習慣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.32,0:17:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這種錯綜複雜的路線\N是不可能飛完的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜\N記得我們的目的並不是獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領先的是我唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人還真好懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機身調整做得還挺不錯的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不會搖晃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎的聲音也很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可得感謝我的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.35,0:18:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來應該是可以\N飛個八小時沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到預定地點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.13,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把速度降低\N我想測量最好的時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，這是任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等第二圈再來行動也不遲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先和那傢伙拉開距離才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近預定地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼還沒到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾還沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去接他好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜機通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一圈12分05秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長她已經完全把目的給忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.18,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩吧，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐你旁邊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.46,0:19:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在場的各位\N歡迎你們大駕光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是地平洞窟的負責人賈卡羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.07,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我們也準備了許多\N可以讓各位眼晴一亮的拍賣品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還請各位慢慢欣賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先看第一件拍賣品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把劍莫非是雷德克里夫的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個紋章相信在座\N應該有很多人都知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是英年早逝的不世出名匠\N雷德克里夫親手所打造的寶劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十分適合作為今夜的開幕珍品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起拍價60萬克勞地亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,65萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.73,0:20:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,67萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,70萬克勞地亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,75萬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼式迴轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才那個迴轉怎樣，魯修拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，線條取的非常漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，接下來是剪式飛行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是費爾邦的項鍊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎都不合你的意是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才就看你\N完全不為所動的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你是有什麼東西要找嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.40,0:20:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你看起來\N似乎也對拍賣沒麼興趣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.87,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經找到\N我想要的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只需要\N把它弄到手就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.65,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接近預定地點\N把速度降低，塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度降低百分之二十
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢從我的頭上飛過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.06,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三，二，一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地點掌握失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不賴嘛，英麥曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EXILE
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信各位都曾經聽說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的存在相當於上帝的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到它就等於得到了整個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過至今從來沒有人\N看過它真正的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們賈卡羅財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.40,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為被選中的各位安排了這個\N據說是可以進入EXILE之門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.27,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚終極的拍賣品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.07,0:21:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.88,0:21:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別老是把我當個病人一樣好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起拍價五百萬克勞地亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千萬克勞地亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千萬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.25,0:22:39.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.02,0:22:46.12,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.19,0:22:51.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.50,0:22:57.30,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.37,0:23:02.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你捨命奮鬥的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.01,0:23:11.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.89,0:23:17.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.72,0:23:23.53,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.60,0:23:29.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:35.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.28,0:23:48.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回預告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.46,0:23:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.36,0:23:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.56,0:23:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不能沒有妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.93,0:23:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管別人怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.37,0:24:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的領航員只有妳拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.93,0:24:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.64,0:24:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這次比賽結束以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.44,0:24:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就打算有件事要跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.37,0:24:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.71,0:24:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第十話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.25,0:24:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,設陷詐騙\NSwindle
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.75,0:24:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定哦，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.99,0:24:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，一言為定
